Reasoning: The paper introduces a neural network architecture for spatio-temporal prediction, which falls under the category of machine learning. The use of recurrent neural networks and parallel, distributed learning suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The focus on neural networks also suggests that it may belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses the modeling of complex dynamics, which is a common topic in the sub-category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of spatio-temporal data and the modeling of causality suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
